title: #OccupyGalleFace marks 58 days
body_lines: COLOMBO (News 1st); The non-partisan people’s struggle in front of the Presidential Secretariat continues for the 58th day, today (5).
The protestors continue their efforts, demanding the President to resign.
Meanwhile, the GotaGoGama branch which was set up in Kandy commemorated its 50th day today.
